@ananace I would expect skopeo and the following test program to behave the same:
```go
package main

import (
	"fmt"
	"net/http"
)

func main() {
	_, err := http.Get("https://www.google.com/")
	if err != nil {
		fmt.Printf("Failed: %s\n", err)
	} else {
		fmt.Println("Succeeded")
	}
}
```

(Run using `go run nameOfFileWithThoseContents`).
